txt.en: You have done much to aid the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh and are now recognized as an ally to their efforts.
Your continued efforts to support An Shêru earns you greater favour with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Ally of the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
You must earn Ally standing with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
